Amazing cake - and here's a new twist: I added 3/4 t of cayenne to the batter (dry ingredients) and 1/2 t to the ganache (to the cream mixture before heating). Added a tingly burn that built over time - incredible. Don't add cayenne to ganache after mixing in chocolate - it'll break.

