Rating: 4
For those folks having trouble with the ganache, try making the ganache as the layers cook. Allow it to cool in the same pot that you cooked it in, stirring every 7-10 minutes. It should be at a nice spreadable consistency by the time your layers are cool. Works for me everytime... =|:-) Ed Kasky

