To really send it over the top, try this walnut filling, courtesy of Shirley Corriher's "Cookwise:" toast 1/2 lb of walnuts, let cool, then whirr in the food processor with 3-4 tablespoons of softened, salted butter. The contrast between the chocolate and the toasted, buttery walnut flavor is remarkable.

