If anyone else is having trouble finding 10 x 2" round cake pans, try the mail order catalogue 'Sweet Celebrations'. They have a huge selection of cake making equipment - much of it professional standard - & these pans are just $9.45 each. Used to be called 'Maid of Scandinavia' & you can call 1-800-328-6722 for a catalogue. The item # for 10 x 2" pans is 606732.

