Rating: 4
WOW! You can't go wrong with this cake - I've made it several times and it is consistently moist, even the time I forgot it in the oven! I've also made it with cream cheese icing and with a white chocolate icing - all to rave reviews and demands for more. It's great with a kaluah whipped cream filling (1/2 c. whipping cream, 1Tbs Kaluah and 1/4c confectioners sugar) Finally, for those without 10" pans it will make three 8" layers or 2 8" layers and cupcakes. Use about three cups of the batter for each 8" layer.

