Rating: 4
I made this for my husband's birthday and it was a huge hit! The cake is extremely moist and the frosting decadent. I didn't have 10" pans so I substituted 3 9 X 1 1/2" pans. I made a two-layer cake with the frosting and saved the third layer to eat as "snack cake". There was just enough frosting to frost between layers and over the top with some falling down over the sides. Really just a perfect amount. If you love chocolate - this is your cake! Slice in small pieces when you serve - it is extremely rich.

